<h2>Patient Transfer Search</h2>
<hr />
<span class="title">Screen Overview </span><br />
<div class="clear"></div>
This screen is basically to search for admitted with the minimum details possible for which the transfer records have to be created. The best search criterion to find out a patient from the database is the HIN or AD no. of the patient. But the same may not be available with the patient. Then the other available information can be used to find out the patient. The search can be multiple criteria and based on Name, Service no., Address, ward, Phone No etc. Once the entry is done the system will search for the required record. If the exact match is not found, then the system will display several records matching the given information. The user will have then to find out the right one by adding more suitable search criteria or by going into the details of the selected records.

